1
00:00:02,635 --> 00:00:04,104
There are no cameras now.

2
00:00:04,571 --> 00:00:06,006
We aren't filming,

3
00:00:06,006 --> 00:00:07,407
and this isn't for promo.

4
00:00:32,198 --> 00:00:33,566
I know how to play the part.

5
00:00:35,168 --> 00:00:36,302
It's just a job, after all.

6
00:00:37,270 --> 00:00:39,706
I look forward to working with you.

7
00:00:41,508 --> 00:00:42,275
Oh, and...

8
00:00:46,913 --> 00:00:48,581
about this prop.

9
00:00:49,482 --> 00:00:50,917
Here, you can have it back.

10
00:01:20,380 --> 00:01:22,215
It's only a job.

11
00:01:22,215 --> 00:01:23,616
Why act like you really mean it?

12
00:01:24,484 --> 00:01:25,718
You almost had me there.

13
00:01:28,688 --> 00:01:31,591
If I let you mess with my head again,

14
00:01:31,591 --> 00:01:33,126
my name isn't Bai.

15
00:01:34,828 --> 00:01:36,296
Stupid Hei Yan. Jerk.

16
00:01:42,235 --> 00:01:44,571
They're a total mismatch.

17
00:01:45,171 --> 00:01:46,306
Don't let Hei Yan's

18
00:01:46,306 --> 00:01:48,808
devoted lover act

19
00:01:48,808 --> 00:01:50,043
fool you.

20
00:01:50,043 --> 00:01:53,046
He's a total fraud.

21
00:01:54,380 --> 00:01:55,748
"Hei-Bai Mercury..."

22
00:01:56,449 --> 00:01:57,984
More like Mercury retrograde!

23
00:02:04,281 --> 00:02:10,303
[Hei Yan is reading the comments
that were just narrated by Bai Xing]
